    "body": "I switched to latest:\n```\n❯ starship --version\nstarship 1.24.1\nbranch:\ncommit_hash:\nbuild_time:2025-11-24 21:18:45 +00:00\nbuild_env:rustc 1.90.0 (1159e78c4 2025-09-14),stable-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu\n```\n\nBut running `starship init fish --print-full-init | source` just leads to a blank prompt\n\n```\nfish_prompt_4.x> starship init fish --print-full-init | source\necho \"hi\"\nhi\n```\n\nEven tried the `1.24.2`:\n```\n❯ starship --version\nstarship 1.24.2\nbranch:master\ncommit_hash:5de07128\nbuild_time:2025-12-30 19:29:54 +00:00\nbuild_env:rustc 1.92.0 (ded5c06cf 2025-12-08),stable-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu\n```",
